	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Master System on Mega Drive ( via Phantasy Star 1 pcb)</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't see any reason why you can't, as long as the pinout is the same (unless you replace the whole PCB). Setting the console into Master System mode is literally just a matter of wiring a line in the cartridge slot (some other lines get repurposed, but as long as you stick to what that cartridge does you should be safe).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


